vernac_cmds: Definition Concyclic A B C D := Coplanar A B C D /\ exists O, Cong O A O B /\ Cong O A O C /\ Cong O A O D.
Lemma concyclic_aux : forall A B C D, Concyclic A B C D -> exists O, Cong O A O B /\ Cong O A O C /\ Cong O A O D /\ Coplanar A B C O.
intros A B C D [HCop [O1]]; spliter.
destruct (l11_62_existence A B C O1) as [O []].
repeat split; try apply cong2_per2__cong with O1 O1; Cong; Cop.
Lemma concyclic_trans : forall A B C D E, ~ Col A B C -> Concyclic A B C D -> Concyclic A B C E -> Concyclic A B D E.
apply coplanar_trans_1 with C; Col; Cop.
apply is_circumcenter_uniqueness with A B C;try assumption.
